The underlying text of *A Course in Miracles* distributed by this
application is the PUBLIC DOMAIN "Sparkly Edition" of the Course, published
by Teddy Poppe (Theodore Poppe) and associated with the Course in Miracles
Society (CIMS). This text descends from the CIMS / Endeavor Academy
lineage that prevailed in Penguin Books USA, Inc. v. New Christian Church
of Full Endeavor, Ltd. (S.D.N.Y. 2003), in which the court held that the
original Course manuscript had entered the public domain because it was
distributed without copyright notice before registration. That text is therefore freely usable by anyone, owned by no
one, and not licensed by this document.

THIS APPLICATION DOES NOT USE, DISTRIBUTE, OR RELY ON THE FOUNDATION FOR
INNER PEACE (FIP) EDITION OR ANY LATER FIP-EDITED EDITION OF THE COURSE.
FIP's added prefaces, supplements, and editorial changes in the Second
Edition and subsequent printings are not present in this application.
This license makes no claim over the public-domain Course text itself and
takes no position on any FIP-edited material, which is separate and outside
the scope of this repository.

